{"tid":1978133,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港共政權夾好口供未？ 【特區政府：中聯辦須按基本法22條遵守香港法律】","createTime":"2020-04-18T13:02:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-18T13:44:24.000Z","uid":136591,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ecdb5aad99f94ec1466e0243f9c720da0ea478e0","tid":1978133,"uid":136591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T13:02:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kGq5mF1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkGq5mF1.png&h=0d1c139a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n琴日兩辦又衝出黎話自己唔係基本法廿二條指既中央部門。宜家港共政權又話係？<br />\n<br />\n另外，原來中共用法律恐嚇議員，強行干擾立法會議程，唔叫干涉香港內政？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我屌你老母，習近平，林鄭月娥。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n手足，我地宜家有咩做既就係：<br />\n一、打國際線：向外國講香港失去自治能力、講今日瘋狂拘捕異見者民主派社運人士。<br />\n（雖然外國忙抗疫，但完抗疫後，呢d一點一滴文宣就會形成巨大力量圍剿中共！）<br />\n二：立會就到！幫手叫人登記做選民！<br />\n三：練體能練體能！<br />\n四： 齊上齊落，不割席，不分化<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">光復香港，時代革命。</span></span>"},{"pid":"2c3392477eaa4e44c75b6a4215eb68c576168113","tid":1978133,"uid":136591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T13:03:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d1b4e5c223fae801434cb24721109679170482f9","tid":1978133,"uid":136591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T13:03:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cd45d0ff24437a50b0f37929df09d707aedecdfb","tid":1978133,"uid":136591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T13:04:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1935cacdebfe4d67e4f4775d4f2362ab8893f0c6","tid":1978133,"uid":66609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T13:05:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8bad97a266b5fab2aa6167532e5b3dca2118a34","tid":1978133,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T13:05:04.000Z","msg":"RTHK不嬲都反政府架啦"},{"pid":"a0729d0dd2860542fb417afa03fed2